{"tid":806761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西鐵線列車延誤　站內通告錯字連連","createTime":"2018-09-05T03:19:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T21:53:57.000Z","uid":39464,"like":252,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":98,"replies":[{"pid":"d30bd766e55e6ec7b6d9ff3262d33311a88817fc","tid":806761,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T03:19:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180905/s00001/8cfa8ee7f10ebc88c24cac4b7f073dae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180905%2Fs00001%2F8cfa8ee7f10ebc88c24cac4b7f073dae.jpg&h=c7e36d9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵西鐵線故障，列車服務受阻，其間不少乘客依靠港鐵站內「車務狀況」通知欄留意最新情況。然而，有乘客卻發現港鐵某車站貼出的車務狀況告示錯別字連連，讓人啼笑皆非。<br />\n<br />\n網民上載的圖片所見，有關告示將南昌站寫作「南晶站」、柯士甸站寫作「枯士甸站」、美孚站則寫作「美乎站」和「美乎王站」，而文末更夾雜口語，稱「你嘅旅程受到延誤」。<br />\n<br />\n帖文一出旋即引起網民討論，有人笑言「人類好神奇，就算你打錯字，我都知你寫乜」；有人借此嘲諷港鐵主席馬時亨，指「個嘢壞咗啊，你明就得啦」；亦有人稱這可能是港鐵的內部叫法，「好似去茶餐廳叫『靚仔』、『零T』一樣」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180905/s00001/1536116934116\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180905%2Fs00001%2F1536116934116&d=475R2aNBn2CFmojb1lVusb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=f6e04dea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180905%2Fs00001%2F1536116934116&h=9c52cc59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180905/s00001/1536116934116</a>"},{"pid":"6391c599a945db5ea793f756a665dced2864d98a","tid":806761,"uid":11719,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T03:19:59.000Z","msg":"無眼睇"},{"pid":"a7362035b8d1796599a4ba4ad19d326c605dd0a6","tid":806761,"uid":178800,"like":3,"dislike":34,"score":-31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T03:20:12.000Z","msg":"召喚月巴糸糸大隻（真人上陣）"},{"pid":"279aecb930db60a3057aa665d725a11c9bcacc41","tid":806761,"uid":199145,"like":66,"dislike":3,"sc